+-nodelist -- Compile FidoNet nodelist to binkd.conf format
+-
+-USAGE:
+-  nodelist <nodelist_file> <domain> [<output_file>]
+-
+-DESCRIPTION:
+-  Reads a FidoNet nodelist and outputs binkd.conf compatible
