+-  nodelist /etc/fido/nodelist.456 fidonet >> binkd.conf
+-  nodelist C:\Fido\NODELIST.001 fidonet C:\Fido\nodes.conf
+-
+-CONFIGURATION FILE:
+-  None. All parameters are command-line arguments.
